high_descs: Walk over to the side of the kitchen island behind you.
Pick up the large metal knife off of the kitchen island.
Look down at the kitchen island.
Slice up the closest head of lettuce on the kitchen island.
Turn right and walk around the kitchen island to the green bin to the left of the oven.
Put the large metal knife in the green bin.
Walk back around to the other side of the kitchen island behind you.
Pick up a piece of sliced lettuce off of the island.
Turn right and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the piece of sliced lettuce inside then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the now chilled piece of sliced lettuce.
Walk over to the oven behind you, then turn left and walk forward, turn right and walk up to the small green bin next to the oven.
Put the chilled piece of sliced lettuce in the green bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled piece of sliced lettuce in a green bin.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the left side of the island.
Pick up the yellow knife from the counter.
Move back away from the island slightly.
Slice the lettuce on the counter.
Turn right and go around the island to the green trash can on the left of the stove.
Place the knife in the trashcan.
Turn around and go back to the side of the island with sliced lettuce.
Pick up one slice of the,lettuce from the counter.
Turn right and go to the refrigerator.
Chill the lettuce in the refrigerator before removing it.
Turn around and go back to the green trash can on the left of the stove.
Place the lettuce in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw out a chilled slice of lettuce.
